annotations.comment:
This is a reference genome for the Human Microbiome Project. This
project is co-owned with the Human Microbiome Project DACC.
Source DNA provided by McDonald, J., Daigneault, M., White, Sibley,
C.D., Strauss, J.C., and Allen-Vercoe, E. (Molecular and Cellular
Biology, University of Guelph, Guelph, Ontario, N1G 2W1, Canada).
Bacteria provided by McDonald, J., Daigneault, M., White, A.,
Sibley, C.D., Strauss, J.C., and Allen-Vercoe, E. (Molecular and
Cellular Biology, University of Guelph, Guelph, Ontario, N1G 2W1,
Canada).
Please be aware that the annotation is done automatically with
little or no manual curation.
Gene Calling Method: GeneMark; Glimmer; Metagene; PFAM; Blast to
non-redundant protein database; Manual curation.

detection_rule: ((cds(Pyr_redox_2 and Oxidored_FMN) or baiCD or baiH) and (minimum(2, [ACD1_car, ACP_syn_III_C, AcetylCoA_hyd_C, AcetylCoA_hydro, Acyl-CoA_dh_1, Acyl-CoA_dh_2, Butyrate_kinase, CT_Propionyl_CoA1, CT_Propionyl_CoA2, CT_Propionyl_CoA3, Carboxyl_trans, CoA_trans, CoA_trans_230_acto, CoA_trans_2_CAF, CoA_trans_6_Glutaconate, E1_dh, ECH_1, ECH_2, HBT, HBT_2, HCDH, HpaB, Ketoacyl-synt_C, Thiolase_C, Thiolase_N, adh_short, adh_short_C2]) or FA_synthesis))
(cds(POR_N and TPP_enzyme_C) and POR and not cds(POR_N and TPP_enzyme_C and POR))
((PFL_acetate1 or PFL_acetate2) and Radical_SAM)

(TPP_enzyme_C and not (PFL-like or PFL_6_pcresol or PFL_9_tma or Gly_radical or Gly_430_pcre or Gly_8-9_TMA or PFL_acetate1 or PFL_acetate2 or Gly_radical_scatole or PFL_proline or PFL_toluene) and minimum(2, [ALS_ss_C, AlaDh_PNT_C, Arginase, BKACE, BcrAD_BadFG, Beta_elim_lyase, CPSase_L_D2, Cys_Met_Meta_PP, ELFV_dehydrog, GRDB, Glu_syn_central, Glu_synthase, Gly_reductase, HAAA1, HG2B1, HG2B2, HGD-D, HleuD1, HleuD2, HleuS1, HleuS2, Homoserine_dh, ILVD_EDD, IlvC, Lactoyl-CoA1, Lactoyl-CoA2, Lyase_aromatic, MAAL_C, OKR_DC_1_5_lysine, OKR_DC_1_5_ornithine, OKR_DC_1_7_arginine, OKR_DC_1_C, OTCace, PALP, Proline_reductase, Sacchrp_dh_C, TPL, Thr_dehydrat_C, TnaA, Urocanase]) and not (POR or POR_N or PFOR_II))
(minimum(1, [PFOR_II, POR, POR_N]) and minimum(2, [CoA_binding, CoA_binding_2, Ligase_CoA, PTAC, Succ_CoA_lig]) and not (Gly_radical_scatole or Gly_radical or Gly_430_pcre or Gly_8-9_TMA))

(minimum(4, [AcetylCoA_hyd_C, AcetylCoA_hydro, B12-binding, Biotin_lipoyl, Glyoxalase_4, HMGL-like, MM_CoA_mutase, MeaB, OAD_beta, OAD_gamma, PYC_OADA]) and minimum(1, [CT_Btheta, CT_Propionyl_CoA1, CT_Propionyl_CoA2, CT_Propionyl_CoA3, CT_Vparvula]) and not Cytidylate_kin)
(Complex1_51K and minimum(5, [FMN_bind, FeS, Fer4, Fer4_9, NQR2_RnfD_RnfE, Rnf-Nqr, RnfC_N, SLBB]))

(minimum(1, [HAAA1, HG2B1, HG2B2, HGD-D, HleuD1, HleuD2, HleuS1, HleuS2, Lactoyl-CoA1, Lactoyl-CoA2]) and minimum(1, [ACP_syn_III, ACP_syn_III_C, AcetylCoA_hyd_C, AcetylCoA_hydro, Acyl-CoA_dh_1, Acyl-CoA_dh_2, AdoHcyase_NAD, AlaDh_PNT_C, BcrAD_BadFG, Biotin_lipoyl, Carboxyl_trans, CoA_trans, CoA_trans_230_acto, CoA_trans_6_Glutaconate, CoA_transf_3, ECH_1, ECH_2, ETF, ETF_alpha, FGGY_C, HCDH, HCDH_N, Hacid_dh, Hacid_dh_C, Mal_decarbox_Al, Peptidase_M22, Peptidase_M23, Thiolase_C, Thiolase_N, ketoacyl-synt]) and not (minimum(2, [AcetylCoA_hyd_C, BcrAD_BadFG, CoA_trans, CoA_trans_230_acto, Mal_decarbox_Al]) and Lactoyl-CoA2 and Lactoyl-CoA1) and not (minimum(4, [ACP_syn_III, ACP_syn_III_C, Acyl-CoA_dh_1, Acyl-CoA_dh_2, AlaDh_PNT_C, BcrAD_BadFG, ECH_1, ECH_2, ETF, ETF_alpha, HCDH, HCDH_N, Hacid_dh, Hacid_dh_C, IlvN, NAD_Gly3P_dh_N, Thiolase_C, Thiolase_N, ketoacyl-synt]) and HAAA1 and not HleuS1))

((minimum(2, [AMP-binding, CoA_transf_3, FAD_binding_2, FAD_oxidored, KR, NAD_binding_8, Pyr_redox, adh_short, adh_short_C2]) and baiH and baiCD) or (minimum(3, [AMP-binding, ATP-grasp_3, ATP-grasp_4, Acyltransferase, CPSase_L_D2, CoA_transf_3, Dala_Dala_lig_C, Dala_Dala_lig_N, FAD_binding_2, FAD_oxidored, GARS_A, GHMP_kinases_C, GHMP_kinases_N, KR, LysM, NAD_binding_8, Pyr_redox, adh_short, adh_short_C2]) and baiH and baiCD))
